ears, but the everyday reality

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:24.420
is we live, work, and
play with an increasing

00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:27.280
amount of environmental noise.

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:31.500
In fact, unwanted sound
is one of the most common

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:33.990
environmental problems.

00:05:33.990 --> 00:05:36.510
It's not only annoying,
but it prevents us

00:05:36.510 --> 00:05:39.880
from understanding our
colleagues, friends,

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:41.400
and loved ones.

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:44.700
No matter how well
we can hear, most of

00:05:44.700 --> 00:05:47.820
