00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:12.850
Accessibility service--
Accessibility Menu

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:15.040
is a new accessibility
service to make

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:18.220
common interactions
easier for users

00:10:18.220 --> 00:10:20.080
with physical disabilities.

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.540
In the US alone,
this is a population

00:10:22.540 --> 00:10:26.950
of over 75 million users.

00:10:26.950 --> 00:10:31.280
Accessibility Menu simplifies
the following functions--

00:10:31.280 --> 00:10:35.890
hardware shortcuts including
power off, lock screen,

00:10:35.890 --> 00:10:38.980
take screenshot,
and volume control;

00:10:38.980 --> 00:10:41.980
