up and swipe down

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:45.660
for recent apps, notifications,
and quick settings.

00:10:45.660 --> 00:10:48.280
It'll also allow you
to invoke the assistant

00:10:48.280 --> 00:10:53.140
or go directly to Accessibility
Settings instantly.

00:10:53.140 --> 00:10:57.340
Further, we designed it with
very large touch targets

00:10:57.340 --> 00:10:59.660
located at the
bottom of the screen.

00:10:59.660 --> 00:11:02.980
This facilitates reachability
for those with smaller hands

00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:04.630
or limited reach.

00:11:04.630 --> 00:11:08.020
It works in both portrait
and landscape mode.

00:11:08.020 --> 00:11:11.740
Lastly, Accessibility
Menu is built on top

00:11:11.740 --> 00:11:13.600
of our accessibility framework.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:17.330
We added two new APIs for
screenshot and lock screen,

00:11:17.330 --> 00:11:20.660
