to test this app,

00:17:14.420 --> 00:17:17.869
go to google.com/accessibility
and sign up to be a trusted

00:17:17.869 --> 00:17:19.310
tester.

00:17:19.310 --> 00:17:23.010
You can come to our sandbox
to see a demo as well.

